CMOS Mirror Adder Implementation
.include "E:\VLSI_ July_Nov_2021\Lab_Work\EXPT 7 Adder\MOSMODEL.TXT"
VDD 1 0 DC 1.8V
VA 14 0 PULSE(0 1.8 0 1N 1N 40U 80U)
VB 15 0 PULSE(0 1.8 0 1N 1N 80U 160U)
VC 16 0 PULSE(0 1.8 0 1N 1N 160U 320U)
M1 4 14 0 0 CMOSN L=0.18U W=2.16U
M2 4 15 0 0 CMOSN L=0.18U W=2.16U
